Package pw.ollie.politics.util.math.geo

Class Cuboid

  • java.lang.Object
    • pw.ollie.politics.util.math.geo.Cuboid
  • public class Cuboid
extends Object
    Represents a cuboid space in a Minecraft world.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors

      Cuboid​(org.bukkit.Location base, org.bukkit.Location opposite)

      Constructs a new Cuboid, with the given Position objects as opposite corners of the Cuboid.
